23 SECTION 6. The unit captions used in this 2026 Act are provided only for the convenience
24 of the reader and do not become part of the statutory law of this state or express any leg-
25 islative intent in the enactment of this 2026 Act.
26 SECTION 7. This 2026 Act being necessary for the immediate preservation of the public
27 peace, health and safety, an emergency is declared to exist, and this 2026 Act takes effect
28 on its passage.
